responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "697749D04996A67E2BB61BA65D2A893D", "Our next move is to learn what that cult is up to.  The Sighted have been concentrating their activity in the Ruins of Sephillion.  That lost city is filled with all manner of demonic and arcane creatures.  We don\'t have the forces to spare to clear them out but I have sent some scouts to keep the area surveyed in case the enemy decides to make a move on us.  If you have the nerve, report to Scout Orithar on the outskirts of Sephillion and do what they ask.")
name: CSQ_DD_0035_SFS_2ndSwordCaptain_10_Response
